Package: pigauto
Title: Phylogenetic Imputation via Graph Autoencoders
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Shinichi", "Nakagawa", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "itchyshin@gmail.com")
Description: Imputes missing species trait data using a Residual Phylogenetic
    Denoising Autoencoder (ResidualPhyloDAE) that combines Brownian-Motion
    phylogenetic imputation (via Rphylopars) with a graph neural network
    residual correction. Because the neural network is constrained to learn
    bounded corrections on top of the BM baseline, imputation quality cannot
    regress below Rphylopars. Includes a 300-species AVONET bird morphology
    subset and a matching BirdTree phylogeny for real-data demonstration.
